    </statement>
    <statement id="425.txt-3">
      <text>blades narrowly oblanceolate, 4–35 × 0.5–4 cm, entire to deeply dentate or lobed (lobes narrow, straight or slightly recurved), faces glabrous or hirsute, hairs usually simple.</text>
